      <title>Cliffs 首席执行官称股票回购比交易更好地利用资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/cliffs-ceo-calls-share-buybacks-better-use-of-money-than-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰克利夫斯公司的最高老板表示，回购股票比收购更有意义——这一观点支撑了这家美国钢铁制造商回购高达 15 亿美元股票的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/cliffs-ceo-calls-share-buybacks-better-use-of-money-than-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:59:21 GMT</pubDate>
